{"tid":2053884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"藍絲：如果唔係暴力示威，政府洗乜用膠水痴著啲磚，觀塘洗乜水浸？","createTime":"2020-06-06T16:19:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T05:41:00.000Z","uid":42188,"like":12,"dislike":303,"uniUserReply":93,"replies":[{"pid":"ed00155ab793750880802b6fea703baab4747949","tid":2053884,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T16:19:19.000Z","msg":"凌晨黑色暴雨下，觀塘及牛頭角水浸嚴重，不少行人路受到損毀。《蘋果》記者發現大雨過後，區內包括牛頭角有部份行人路嚴重損毀，估計總計數以百計的地磚「浮起」，令部份行人路「破裂」，場面罕見，而「浮起」的明顯是由多塊小地磚「黏合」而成的「膠水地磚」。有區內居民懷疑，政府近年以阻止抗爭者擲地磚為原由，未經諮詢便強行在全港多處行人路以膠水把大量地磚黏起來，令到地磚疏水用的縫隙被封，才導致今日大雨中水浸加劇，致出現上述罕見的大段行人路壞情況。有專家更指行人路斜路的大幅「膠水地磚」，若在大雨中遇地下水，有機會整幅膠水磚滾下斜路，恐對路人或車輛造成危險。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200606/J653JR7BXT2I7ULGXVCSQB4IQQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200606%2FJ653JR7BXT2I7ULGXVCSQB4IQQ%2F&d=bCxsXTpKmrqj5N4FYztdx0uhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=cbfd2436\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200606%2FJ653JR7BXT2I7ULGXVCSQB4IQQ%2F&h=a7b319df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200606/J653JR7BXT2I7ULGXVCSQB4IQQ/</a>"},{"pid":"85510eefa69d2e0025bcb49ef6474c47b2bd0191","tid":2053884,"uid":345458,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T16:20:49.000Z","msg":"請試着說：「七一大遊行」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2053885\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2053885</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"05975c6b611d47c3467091970e0e44a00eee55c1","tid":2053884,"uid":276440,"like":75,"dislike":1,"score":74,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T16:21:44.000Z","msg":"沒有暴徒，只有暴政！"},{"pid":"9daf4f7afdb61e354722df3b532c63c5fb309238","tid":2053884,"uid":228143,"like":256,"dislike":2,"score":254,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T16:24:22.000Z","msg":"如果冇落雨  洗咩有水？？<br />\n<br />\n鬥膠？？"},{"pid":"26ba3d8546babf24c84aeeb704f5fc02a41d3c02","tid":2053884,"uid":8482,"like":150,"dislike":0,"score":15